thread.title: Lesa Boersch
thread.title_full: Burgers' Smokehouse reviewed by Lesa Boersch

author: Lesa Boersch
title: Lesa Boersch
text:
first time ordering 2 different meats online - very impressed with how it was packaged and delivered in coolers with ice packets from yet another state.
However, the quality was very good but not like the best ever.
But then it is previously frozen so to be expected to some point.
I will try more from this company in the future because they
are on spot with delivering a good product in a timely manner!
